==Esperanto==
===Ending===
'''-a'''

# related to, in the manner of, of. (Ending for all [[adjective]]s in Esperanto.)
# belonging to, of. (Ending for all [[possessive]] [[pronoun]]s in Esperanto.)
# -kind of. (Ending of all [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlatives]] of kind in Esperanto.)

===Derived terms===
# related to, in the manner of, of
#* ''[[bela]]'': '''of''' beauty, [[beautiful]]
#* ''[[dekstra]]'': '''of''' the right [direction] (''[[dekstro]]'') [as opposed to left], to the [[right]]
#* ''[[vera]]'': '''of''' truth (''[[vero]]''), [[true]]
# belonging to, of
#* ''[[mia]]'': '''of''' me, [[my]]
#* ''[[via]]'': '''of''' you, [[your]]
#* ''[[lia]]'': '''of''' him, [[his]]
#* ''[[ŝia]]'': '''of''' her, [[her]] [possessive]
#* ''[[ĝia]]'': '''of''' it, [[its]]
#* ''[[nia]]'': '''of''' us, [[our]]
#* ''[[ilia]]'': '''of''' them, [[their]]
# kind of
#* ''[[kia]]'': what '''kind of'''
#* ''[[tia]]'': that '''kind of'''
#* ''[[ĉia]]'': all '''kinds of'''
#* ''[[ia]]'': some '''kind of'''
#* ''[[nenia]]'': no '''kind of'''

